Name: Me
Message: Hey man, this is Andrew Konoff - I'll be moving into your unit in March. Mark said you had some stuff you wanted to sell?

Name: David
Message: Hi Andrew! Yes I do, i have a couch, table and chairs, bedframe, a dresser, a few other odds and ends

Name: David
Message: If you remember the place pretty much everything is for sale, but some had already gone

Name: Me
Message: Awesome. I may be game to grab the bed frame, the dining table and chairs, and possibly a few other things. I'm trying to think of the best way to do this - do you have a list of prices and stuff you could send me?

Name: Me
Message: Awesome. If you can just email what you've got to andrew.konoff@gmail.com, I'd be grateful.

Name: David
Message: Sounds good, I'll email you later this afternoon
